{"tid":464984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我姪仔問我點解噓國歌要坐監，恐嚇殺人同選舉失實就乜事都無","createTime":"2017-11-11T05:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T03:55:18.000Z","uid":149494,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0545482010d571afaa7f86b280efea181dcc6242","tid":464984,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"咁我姪仔就係d幾有critical thinking, 讀書幾叻幾醒目果d細路仔黎，細細個已經會睇新聞同留意時事<br />\n<br />\n今日佢睇到關於國歌法既新聞，就問我點解噓國歌咁小事就要坐監又盛，之前呀何律師公開話要殺人同選舉失實陳述就可以乜事都無<br />\n<br />\n咁佢老母聽到之後就諗住stop佢,話細路仔唔知咁多架啦之類<br />\n<br />\n但我就咁答佢︰因為呀何律師代表權勢同利益的一方，所以無論佢做乜都唔會有事，你第日大個計住要痴埋d權貴度先有運行，有利益就一定要痴埋去奶，到時你講乜都得，做乜都得，千奇唔好諗住社會有公義做個正直既人，唔好做傻仔，明未？<br />\n<br />\n咁佢老豆老母聽到我咁講當堂面都青埋，但又唔知點反應<br />\n<br />\n但姪仔就好醒咁答&quot;我明啦&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我就知佢第日實有運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52b01748e411200b5c8d23052858b3fc49e9027","tid":464984,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5317eb78361b7d50e65f9b55ba731c164728ad","tid":464984,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5524d61c5b2a77bfdc7d5a67b42e6849353ecb5d","tid":464984,"uid":106430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"醒目仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b565a8996938e36f7084d62367c91b66ad1c91","tid":464984,"uid":63976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13329bd55abeb9aa0dd53bef77c22094e8529b1","tid":464984,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44e11b5528d863b9ac408cd54a0a59b4815a8c